@DATABASE "Vixen"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - V - Vixen"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - V
                   ====================================

                                   Vixen
                                   =====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(51858,128)"}          51858,x (x= 1-128)
@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(57541,0)"}          57541,0
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(51789,183)"}          51789,183


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
